        <updateDate>2022-08-08T17:04:20Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Certainty for General Aviation Pilots Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill deems that individuals who provide flight instruction or testing (including phased testing of experimental aircraft) are not operating an aircraft carrying persons or property for hire. Under current law, individuals must generally obtain a regulatory exemption or other authority to deviate from regulatory requirements to provide compensated flight training or testing.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
